fields.description: The aggregated value over the given aggregation interval starting from the intervalStartDateTime. The value is caculated at the minute level. The value at the starting minute of the intervalStartDateTime is included. The value at the last minute of the given interval is excluded. For example, if intervalStartDateTime is 2023-09-20T18:00:00Z and aggregation interval is 5 minutes, then the value is aggregated from 2023-09-20T18:00:00Z(inclusive) to 2023-09-20T18:05:00Z(exclusive).
